resp.text: Thank you Jake!! We appreciate you coming in!

name: Kellie Travers
text:
I came in today to get my sons hair cut, but unfortunately I had to leave before it was our turn. I wasn't expecting too long of a wait, but I was wrong...lol
These ladies are busy little bees! I love seeing the small shops in our town so active. Very friendly and seem to be well liked by all. It is a small shop, but it works. By the way, I love the old antique vanity you have up on display...awesome!
Ladies, I will be back for his next haircut and ill make sure I have time to spare in case there is a wait!

resp.text: Kellie, We thank You for your loyaltee, we work hard to get every one In and Out as fast and as we possibly can. Hope to see u next time. ☺

text: Best Barbers around. Both are great with men's hair as well as women's. I highly recommend them!

name: Jon A
text: Cut N Up Barber & Styles is the GREATEST. I mean Perfect haircut each and everytime and the staff is so friendly and Amazing I’m definitely recommending any and everybody to go here for you’re next haircut be you man woman or child they can do it all. It’s just an all around EPIC place for anything styles highlights haircuts etc. I’d give them 10 stars if I could 🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟 I guess I can lol. But trust me u won’t be disappointed 😁👍 if you don’t believe go there yourself you’ll see what I mean.

name: Tabitha Long
text: Literally the best lawyer! Someone answered the phone every time I called, they were always friendly, and worked with me every step of the way. When the other person was VERY difficult, Blane got me through it and calmed my nerves at every point in the case. Very smart, very professional, and excellent at what he does!

name: Kim Howell
text: Great person to talk with and help you with any of your legal needs.

name: Maranda Hallman
text: very professional and trustworthy . couldn't ask for anyone better

name: Renee Ridgeway
text: This by far has been one of the most horrible situations with an agency I have encountered.  They are very unprofessional, rude, and very unhelpful.  Even if you are willing to make payments they are not willing to work with you in any type of way.  They even refused me the right to speak with the attorney handling the case, yet when i call to pay the account in full the staffs demeanor is totally different.  Nothing good to say about your agency at all.  I wish people trying had another option because you are definitely not it.

name: Alexander Romei
text:
Slime of the Earth. Predatory collections attorney who fails to contact defendants and pushes judgments through to quickly too maximize profits.

Crook by Webster's definition.

name: Cody Yocum
text:
Crooks with no respect. Paid them in full and here we are 3 weeks later I am still having garnishments hit my pay roll. Only answer I can get from them is we have your money and the court will tell us when to give it back.

Pathetic lot of people work at this establishment!

name: Theresa Abner
text: They have done an outstanding job with the accounts that our company has placed with them.  I am extremely pleased with the service we receive.

name: PHeNoM iL DuCe
text: THEY SUCK. Rude customer service - they lie to you and then leave notes in your account saying the opposite of what you were told. They threaten you with the assumption that you're an idiot. They literally mis-entered my information, after processing, admitted to messing it up, then told me they would give me a call. Never got that call. Good job waldrop and associates. Or NOT.

name: Kelly Blankenship
text: Very rude associates very unhelpful. Lady there was speaking as if I was stupid. I wouldn't advise her working there any longer.

name: John Ashworth
text: No one will answer the phone.
